Canonical website:
  http://glade.gnome.org/

Canonical download:
  ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/gnome/sources/glade3/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack glade3-3.6.7-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./glade3-3.6.7-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/glade3-3.6.7-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/glade3-3.6.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/glade3-gnome-3.6.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/glade3-python-3.6.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libgladeui1-devel-3.6.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libgladeui1_9-3.6.7-X.tar.bz2

